name: I'm Tom Yum Kung
description:
Today, Mee will bring friends to eat Tom Yum Kung. Tom Yum Kung is the national dish of Thailand. It is sour and spicy. It is another menu that should not be missed when coming to Thailand. The big prawns and the soup were very tasty, I was hungry too.

What kind of food do you like? Let's exchange menus.
